27
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:03,640
President Fu, what made you suddenly think of inviting Hanqing over for drinks tonight?

28
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:06,400
Well, Director Liang has contributed so much to Royal View Garden.

29
