I can't smile.

76
00:05:20,739 --> 00:05:23,220
Smile anyway.

77
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:32,360
I...

78
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:42,819
Are you okay, honey?

79
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:45,800
Come here, let me see.

80
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,379
Come over here.

81
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:51,780
Are you all right?

82
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:55,000
Don't move.

83
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,879
Hug me.

84
00:05:57,879 --> 00:06:00,100
Hug me, quick!

85
00:06:10,539 --> 00:06:14,459
Now. Immediately. Come to the lounge right away.

86
