126
00:10:33,399 --> 00:10:35,679
I hope I didn't disturb your treasured time with your husband.

127
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:39,139
It's fine, President Fu. It's part of my job.

128
00:10:39,139 --> 00:10:40,580
Have a seat.

129
